I'm deeply pained

291
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:12,399
and I deeply regret my actions.

292
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,000
I sincerely apologize.

293
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:15,159
I'm sorry.

294
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:17,679
By Bai Enyu.

295
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,519
I sincerely apologize to you.

296
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:24,000
If you don't forgive me,

297
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:26,279
(Xia Qiu)
I can write another 5,000-word letter.

298
00:14:26,279 --> 00:14:27,360
I-It's not a problem.

299
00:14:33,799 --> 00:14:34,960
What was that?

300
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:36,200
I signed.

301
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:37,519
I forgive you.

302
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,440
Let's go.

303
00:14:53,759 --> 00:14:54,919
He's quite sincere.

304
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,399
Actually, he is

305
00:14:57,399 --> 00:14:58,799
quite good with kids.

306
00:14:59,039 --> 00:15:00,480
He knows what they are thinking.

307
00:15:02,279 --> 00:15:02,919
That's good.

308
00:15:03,799 --> 00:15:04,352
Well...

309
00:15:04,519 --> 00:15:06,480
Next time you do a late-night outreach,

310
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:07,639
can you take us along?

311
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:09,399
You're interested?

312
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:14,120
Preventing juvenile delinquency

313
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,120
is also

314
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,399
an important part of our work.

315
00:15:16,399 --> 00:15:17,919
You're concerned about them.

316
00:15:18,759 --> 00:15:20,320
Good, I support you.

317
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,879
You should reach out to the kids

318
00:15:22,879 --> 00:15:23,879
and blend in with them.

319
00:15:23,879 --> 00:15:24,919
Or you won't know

320
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,039
what they are thinking.

321
00:15:26,639 --> 00:15:27,519
Tag along next time.

322
00:15:27,639 --> 00:15:28,480
Okay, thanks.

323
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:29,240
No problem.

324
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,080
Wait.

325
00:15:30,919 --> 00:15:32,399
What happened to Tian Jun?

326
00:15:32,399 --> 00:15:33,320
Prosecutor Yuan

327
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,440
has prosecuted him

328
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,480
with illegal detention.

329
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,919
He will pay the price.

330
00:15:44,559 --> 00:15:45,360
Hello, Captain Du.

331
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,879
Prosecutor Lin, you're right.

332
00:15:48,159 --> 00:15:50,399
Someone instigated Chen Huiwen
to commit suicide.

333
00:15:50,519 --> 00:15:52,519
And you know that person.

334
00:15:58,799 --> 00:16:00,399
You really don't need me there?

335
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:01,559
No.

336
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:03,240
I can handle my own matters.

337
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,559
How is that woman doing?

338
00:16:08,399 --> 00:16:09,360
Wenxuan's mom

339
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:11,960
and I sometimes text each other

340
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,480
to say hi.

341
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,600
We'll leave the rest to time.

342
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:19,080
Don't be so harsh on yourself.

343
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,159
Get over it.

344
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:23,679
Let me bear my responsibilities

345
00:16:24,159 --> 00:16:25,639
from now on.

346
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:26,799
Okay?

347
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,639
Prosecutor Zheng told me.

348
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:29,960
You took on

349
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:32,279
all the responsibility regarding this.

350
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:33,919
Thank you.

351
00:16:34,639 --> 00:16:35,559
No problem.

352
00:16:35,559 --> 00:16:37,159
Aren't we in the same department?

353
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,399
Once you start
handling cases independently,

354
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,240
bear all the responsibilities.

355
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:43,159
I'll stay out of it.

356
00:16:45,639 --> 00:16:46,720
I hope so.

357
00:16:47,879 --> 00:16:49,240
Actually, I know my problem.

358
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:51,679
I always tend to "jump over"

359
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,000
procedural justice.

360
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,240
Go hurdle jumping

361
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,440
if you like doing it.

362
00:16:58,039 --> 00:16:59,519
All those who study law know

363
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:00,919
the fruit of the poisonous trees.

364
00:17:01,159 --> 00:17:02,360
It means

365
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:04,160
if you obtain evidence through

366
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,000
improper means,

367
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:07,359
even if it eventually turns the tide,

368
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:08,640
it's toxic.

369
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:11,240
You can't pursue true justice like this.

370
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:14,640
I know sometimes I am a bit rigid.

371
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,799
But if one day, someone finds fault

372
00:17:17,799 --> 00:17:18,559
with

373
00:17:18,559 --> 00:17:20,559
your evidence-gathering procedure,

374
00:17:20,559 --> 00:17:22,640
all your efforts will come to nothing.

375
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:25,559
This is what upsets me the most.

376
00:17:26,279 --> 00:17:27,640
The bad guy is right there.

377
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,400
The fact is so clear.

378
00:17:29,599 --> 00:17:30,480
But to convict him,

379
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,680
it requires so much effort,

380
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,160
so many documents,

381
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,440
so much persuasion,

382
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,400
and so much evidence.

383
00:17:35,759 --> 00:17:36,720
It's too difficult.

384
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:41,039
Remember the day
when Xiaohua and Xiaohu's case

385
00:17:41,039 --> 00:17:42,279
reached a verdict?

386
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,000
Tell me

387
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:44,960
how you felt.

388
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,480
Satisfied.

389
00:17:50,359 --> 00:17:51,359
But also very sad.

390
00:17:54,359 --> 00:17:56,400
Just remember that feeling.

391
00:18:18,039 --> 00:18:19,119
You remember her?

392
00:18:22,279 --> 00:18:23,319
Is her guardian here?

393
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:24,599
Forget it.

394
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:27,000
We didn't ask her to come.

395
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:28,920
We just made a phone call

396
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,240
to confirm some facts.

397
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,759
She came on her own

398
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,079
and confessed.

399
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,000
I checked her ID card.

400
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:36,359
She's under 14.

401
00:18:37,759 --> 00:18:39,240
I wonder what these kids

402
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,119
are thinking.

403
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:43,160
You may leave.

404
00:18:45,279 --> 00:18:46,640
A kind reminder.

405
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,880
I can't see through this child.

406
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,039
But I can be sure of one thing.

407
00:18:53,599 --> 00:18:55,160
She's after you.

408
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,000
Captain Du.

409
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,160
Here.

410
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:12,440
I'm from the Yunhai Procuratorate.

411
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,279
I'm Lin Zhitao.

412
00:19:13,839 --> 00:19:14,599
We need to wait

413
00:19:14,599 --> 00:19:16,000
until your family arrives...

414
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,559
Don't you know where my family is?

415
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,759
We need to wait

416
00:19:23,759 --> 00:19:25,359
until your guardian arrives

417
00:19:25,359 --> 00:19:26,440
to learn about

418
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:28,359
Chen Huiwen's suicide from you.

419
00:19:28,359 --> 00:19:29,000
No need.

420
00:19:29,799 --> 00:19:31,319
Ask away if you want.

421
00:19:33,559 --> 00:19:34,839
- Call him again.
- Okay.

422
00:19:34,839 --> 00:19:36,359
I made Chen Huiwen do it.

423
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,079
I kept her company

424
00:19:39,079 --> 00:19:41,039
as if I was Zhang Wenxuan's shadow.

425
00:19:41,759 --> 00:19:43,519
I posted those things on Weibo.

426
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:46,240
I taught her how to make a fuss,

427
00:19:47,799 --> 00:19:48,640
including the jump.

428
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:51,319
I will avenge you.

429
00:19:55,599 --> 00:19:57,119
I'm Zhang Wenxuan's classmate.

430
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:17,799
Tong.

431
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,319
Actually, I don't understand

432
00:20:21,079 --> 00:20:23,359
why you hate Lin Zhitao so much.

433
00:20:23,359 --> 00:20:25,440
It was Lin Zhitao
who caused my family's ruin.

434
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,240
Then

435
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:28,440
what should we do next?

436
00:20:29,559 --> 00:20:31,359
We have already done our best.

437
00:20:31,359 --> 00:20:32,319
That's the way it is.

438
00:20:32,319 --> 00:20:33,720
Did you try your best?

439
00:20:34,319 --> 00:20:35,279
Did you try your best?

440
00:20:35,759 --> 00:20:36,839
You liar!

441
00:20:37,119 --> 00:20:38,319
- What are you doing?
- Liar.

442
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,279
It's all your fault.

443
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:48,039
You are guilty. Do you know that?

444
00:20:48,839 --> 00:20:50,759
You hold power over others' destinies.

445
00:20:50,759 --> 00:20:51,519
You spare sinners

446
00:20:51,519 --> 00:20:52,319
and harm victims.

447
00:20:52,319 --> 00:20:53,559
You are a murderer.

448
00:20:53,559 --> 00:20:54,559
Calm down.

449
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,440
Ning Kaitong.

450
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:57,920
I've explained

451
00:20:58,079 --> 00:21:00,400
everything to you
about your mother's case.

452
00:21:00,839 --> 00:21:02,200
My mom was innocent.

453
00:21:03,599 --> 00:21:05,559
She just didn't want my dad
to suffer anymore.

454
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,799
She didn't kill anyone.

455
00:21:09,267 --> 00:21:13,039
(Yunhai Intermediate People's Court)
(Trade Union Committee)

456
00:21:13,039 --> 00:21:13,559
Where's Mom?

457
00:21:13,559 --> 00:21:14,440
Why isn't she out?

458
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,480
Where did she go?

459
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:16,920
You don't need to know.

460
00:21:17,519 --> 00:21:18,599
Lawyer, please tell me.

461
00:21:18,599 --> 00:21:19,400
Where is my mom?

462
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,039
When back?

463
00:21:20,039 --> 00:21:21,960
Stop making a scene, okay?

464
00:21:22,599 --> 00:21:23,400
Miss.

465
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,920
Tell me. Where is my mom?

466
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,200
Why the arrest?

467
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,279
She did nothing wrong.

468
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:29,160
Go home. Take care of her.

469
00:21:29,799 --> 00:21:30,839
I'm not going home.

470
00:21:30,839 --> 00:21:32,160
I'll wait for my mom.

471
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:32,680
Be good.

472
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:33,480
No!

473
00:21:33,759 --> 00:21:34,440
Stop it.

474
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:37,119
I'll wait for my mom.

475
00:21:37,119 --> 00:21:38,000
Be good.

476
00:21:39,559 --> 00:21:40,160
Tong.

477
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:40,799
Crime committed.

478
00:21:40,799 --> 00:21:42,319
How can she go home?

479
00:21:42,519 --> 00:21:43,759
Tong.

480
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,359
Tong.

481
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:25,160
Everything was

482
00:22:25,599 --> 00:22:28,880
legal and compliant from filing
to sentencing recommendation

483
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,759
and verdict

484
00:22:30,759 --> 00:22:32,119
regarding your mom's case.

485
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:34,359
You just keep saying
it's "legal and compliant".

486
00:22:34,359 --> 00:22:35,799
What else can you say?

487
00:22:36,519 --> 00:22:37,799
Does legal mean it's right?

488
00:22:37,799 --> 00:22:39,960
Do you know how much she was suffering?

489
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:42,319
Why did you arrest her?

490
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:44,160
Ning Kaitong.

491
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:46,200
Tell us.

492
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,799
What is right and what is wrong?

493
00:22:49,559 --> 00:22:50,720
Listen to us.

494
00:22:51,599 --> 00:22:53,039
Stop going to Chen Huiwen.

495
00:22:55,519 --> 00:22:56,440
Scared of trouble?

496
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,839
Scared she'll kill herself?

497
00:22:59,759 --> 00:23:01,079
Or scared of losing your future?

498
00:23:01,079 --> 00:23:03,079
Leave the innocent ones out of it, okay?

499
00:23:03,079 --> 00:23:04,680
My mom has been in prison for a year.

500
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:07,119
Her hair has turned gray.

501
00:23:08,079 --> 00:23:08,720
And I?

502
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:11,519
I became homeless.

503
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:13,039
I have nothing left.

504
00:23:13,039 --> 00:23:14,799
Yeah, you did your job.

505
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,839
But you ruined me.

506
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:21,839
What do you mean "we ruined you", kid?

507
00:23:23,599 --> 00:23:24,880
If your uncle had written

508
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:27,240
a letter of understanding
for your mom, I...

509
00:23:32,519 --> 00:23:33,519
Procedure is unlawful.

510
00:23:33,519 --> 00:23:34,319
Rain check.

511
00:23:44,279 --> 00:23:45,880
Prosecutor Lin, I just don't get it.

512
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:46,559
Why can't you

513
00:23:46,559 --> 00:23:48,160
just tell her the truth?

514
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:50,359
How long are you
going to be the scapegoat?

515
00:23:51,759 --> 00:23:52,960
I promised her mom.

516
00:23:53,559 --> 00:23:54,119
Captain Du.

517
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:58,759
This is Ning Kaitong's guardian,
Ning Guochang.

518
00:23:58,759 --> 00:23:59,359
Our Captain Du.

519
00:23:59,359 --> 00:24:00,599
I've heard a lot about you.

520
00:24:00,599 --> 00:24:01,599
Save it.

521
00:24:01,599 --> 00:24:03,079
Why didn't you answer the call?

522
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:04,480
Want us to pay you a visit?

523
00:24:04,799 --> 00:24:06,279
How could I dare?

524
00:24:06,279 --> 00:24:07,559
I was really busy.

525
00:24:07,559 --> 00:24:08,200
Busy?

526
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:10,079
What's more important, work or the kid?

527
00:24:10,079 --> 00:24:11,640
The kid. The kid is important.

528
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,160
It won't happen again.

529
00:24:15,119 --> 00:24:16,000
Remember her?

530
00:24:16,519 --> 00:24:19,200
This is Prosecutor Lin Zhitao
from the procuratorate.

531
00:24:20,079 --> 00:24:21,079
Prosecutor Lin.

532
00:24:21,279 --> 00:24:22,880
Sorry for causing you trouble.

533
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:24,319
Did she stop going to school?

534
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:28,720
She's skipping classes. What can I do?

535
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:29,400
As her guardian,

536
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,799
you have to do something.

537
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:33,400
Send her back to school, understand?

538
00:24:33,559 --> 00:24:34,599
Yeah, I understand.

539
00:24:34,799 --> 00:24:35,400
Rest assured.

540
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:36,559
I'll keep an eye on her.

541
00:24:37,519 --> 00:24:39,160
Alright, go back to work.

542
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,240
I will keep you updated.

543
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:40,839
Okay.

544
00:24:41,599 --> 00:24:42,119
Take care.

545
00:24:43,839 --> 00:24:44,519
Captain Du.

546
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:46,559
Why did you ask me to come?

547
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:48,960
Did you tell him?

548
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:49,920
Yeah.

549
00:24:50,279 --> 00:24:51,559
Why are you playing dumb?

550
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,119
Receive the admonition.

551
00:24:55,559 --> 00:24:56,200
Let's go.

552
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:11,200
I'm warning you.

553
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:12,519
Stay away from him.

554
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,400
Who are you to him?

555
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,240
Why do you care?

556
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:22,480
If you show up again,

557
00:25:23,119 --> 00:25:24,279
I'll kill you.

558
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:27,240
I offered him food out of kindness.

559
00:25:27,599 --> 00:25:28,599
What did I do wrong?

560
00:25:28,599 --> 00:25:30,000
Come on, kill me.

561
00:25:30,319 --> 00:25:31,799
I dare you to kill me now.

562
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,000
Calm down.

563
00:25:40,359 --> 00:25:41,200
Who are you?

564
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:43,319
Calm down.

565
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:46,039
We can talk it through.

566
00:25:46,359 --> 00:25:48,240
Both of you, stay away from him.

567
00:25:48,559 --> 00:25:49,559
Did you hear me?

568
00:25:57,792 --> 00:25:58,400
Let's go.

569
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,319
What's your problem?

570
00:26:04,319 --> 00:26:05,359
Where were you when he was

571
00:26:05,359 --> 00:26:06,440
digging in the trash can?

572
00:26:07,119 --> 00:26:08,880
Yeah, I've got a problem.

573
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:10,480
So what?

574
00:26:11,599 --> 00:26:12,880
I'll let you off this time.

575
00:26:13,640 --> 00:26:15,240
Let's see what happens next time.

576
00:26:23,599 --> 00:26:24,319
You lunatic.

577
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,480
Enough.

578
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:35,200
Who is she? What's her problem?

579
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:36,880
I don't know.

580
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:39,000
