882
00:37:50,199 --> 00:37:51,440
Can you tell?

883
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:54,400
They don't even check IDs.

884
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,679
Everyone can come in.

885
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,079
They drink as if

886
00:37:58,079 --> 00:37:59,079
there's no tomorrow.

887
00:37:59,079 --> 00:38:00,119
Once they get drunk,

888
00:38:00,119 --> 00:38:02,159
anything might happen.

889
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,280
Can we submit a proposal

890
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:08,559
to the Administration
of Industry and Commerce?

891
00:38:08,559 --> 00:38:09,960
Do you think it'll work?

892
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,800
If it can be implemented, yeah.

893
00:38:13,239 --> 00:38:15,239
But it takes time, doesn't it?

894
00:38:15,239 --> 00:38:16,800
So what can we do now?

895
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:18,280
Keep being friends with them.

896
00:38:19,599 --> 00:38:20,599
What about

897
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:21,880
calling the police?

898
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:23,639
Inform their parents.

899
00:38:23,639 --> 00:38:24,639
Tell them about it.

900
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,599
They're hanging out here

901
00:38:26,599 --> 00:38:27,960
because their parents don't care

902
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:29,719
or can't manage them, right?

903
00:38:30,079 --> 00:38:30,760
They'll be out

904
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:32,000
even if you put them in.

905
00:38:32,239 --> 00:38:33,679
