906
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,760
- Right?
- Yeah, got it.

907
00:38:36,039 --> 00:38:36,679
Then I can't

908
00:38:36,679 --> 00:38:37,800
help with anything.

909
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:39,239
Makes sense.

910
00:38:39,719 --> 00:38:40,559
You're pretty sly.

911
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,079
Just a little bit.

912
00:38:42,719 --> 00:38:43,719
But kids these days

913
00:38:43,719 --> 00:38:44,840
really need

914
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,159
trustworthy adults around them.

915
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:49,199
If they feel abandoned and that no one

916
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,519
cares about them,

917
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:52,679
they'll just go their own way.

918
00:38:52,960 --> 00:38:54,079
Then it'll be too late.

919
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:57,960
So what can we do now?

920
00:38:57,960 --> 00:38:59,239
Make sure these kids

921
00:38:59,239 --> 00:39:00,280
don't go to you.

922
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:01,360
Then it'll be too late.

923
00:39:01,719 --> 00:39:02,480
Why?

924
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,639
What's wrong with us?

925
00:39:03,639 --> 00:39:04,920
Yeah, how can you tell?

926
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,000
Look at this necklace.

927
00:39:06,559 --> 00:39:07,719
- Look how she dances.
