Yeah, I'm just like them.

935
00:39:17,719 --> 00:39:18,440
Totally.

936
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:19,159
Yeah.

937
00:39:19,519 --> 00:39:21,039
You have no self-awareness at all.

938
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:23,199
- What?
- Nothing. You're awesome.

939
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:24,159
