944
00:39:33,159 --> 00:39:34,039
I'm meeting someone.

945
00:39:34,039 --> 00:39:35,039
I'll just...

946
00:39:35,159 --> 00:39:36,440
Don't you always wear makeup?

947
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:37,800
No, I never do.

948
00:39:39,039 --> 00:39:40,679
- Go home early.
- Don't be late tomorrow.

949
00:39:40,864 --> 00:39:41,400
Okay.

